pageContext.claim: “You know, he [Putin] helped us with the oil industry, which was good for him, too. But we got it up, and now we're going to save millions of jobs in Texas and North Dakota and other places, Oklahoma with millions of jobs. I mean, the oil now is sustainable. I mean, it was down to zero, which would have ruined -- we would have lost five million jobs, but no. It's not a question of what he's done.”
pageContext.analysis: Vladimir Putin did not save 5 million oil jobs in the United States.
